data.description: Welcome home! This home has so many amazing features. Where to begin? Great family home with open floor plan, laminate flooring throughout main level, and plenty of space inside and outside. New Frigidaire  stainless appliances and oven/air fryer combo in the kitchen 2023, new hot water heater 2023, Trane HVAC 2020, new furnace in 2017 new salt water pool and patio area 2019, new Hot tub 2021. Home has 3 bedrooms and a huge bonus room over the garage that could be used for 4th bedroom b/c of the new closet. Don't forget about the formal dining room and the den off the living room. Also the garage has work door and extra room for tinkering as well. Large master suite with walk in closet, his/her sinks, separate shower and a relaxing jetted soaking tub. What more can you ask for? Schedule your showing today!!
